Maintainer: Reto Burgin <rbuergin@gmx.ch>
Description: Provides tools for estimating and visualizing hierarchical conjoint models for rating-based data. Supports multi-level modeling of individual and group levels, calculation of part-worth utilities, model comparison with likelihood ratio test and stepwise model selection process. Inspired by methodological foundations presented in Applied Conjoint Analysis by Vithala R. Rao (2014).
